{"tid":1909593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會邀錄製抗疫歌　TVB周栢豪菊梓喬等合唱","createTime":"2020-03-04T05:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T14:43:10.000Z","uid":142878,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d880ba7cdd1eb178d78dd11d01af45b0ea4a2a5b","tid":1909593,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">律師會</span></span></strong>邀錄製抗疫歌 周栢豪菊梓喬等合唱<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎來襲，各行各業大受打擊，香港律師會認為，目前需要注入正能量，鼓勵香港市民和醫護界人士打氣。經過過去數星期與不同製作單位聯絡，最終得到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVB</span></span></strong>星夢娛樂集團有限公司同意，合作錄製打氣歌《疫境同行》，星夢會派出旗下十幾名歌手合唱，包括周栢豪、菊梓喬、吳若希、連詩雅等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次活動由香港律師會會長彭韻僖、副會長陳澤銘、前會長蘇紹聰、理事湯文龍及朱潔冰秘書長組成的籌委會<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">牽頭</span></strong></span>，邀請到香港醫學會、香港建築師學會等九個專業團體作支持機構，並得到香港作曲家及作詞家協會的支持共同參與。<br />\n<br />\n律師會多謝無線電視音樂發展事務暨星夢娛樂行政總裁何哲圖在構思和策劃方面與籌備小組深入溝通，又認同他們的方向，協助於歌詞上表達心意，尤其是專業人士應堅守崗位、伸出援手、保守香港，為香港人打氣，為社會注入正能量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1714596/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1714596%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeISVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=a658e971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1714596%2F&h=3d1145fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1714596/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無大律師公會<br />\n你個律師會同林鄭一樣啦, 做show"},{"pid":"3b0b96d4fb545bec9c7543665292f32fef509dfa","tid":1909593,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200304/_2020030408501713279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200304%2F_2020030408501713279.jpg&h=4658cc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200304/_2020030408501758546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200304%2F_2020030408501758546.jpg&h=640e457f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200304/_2020030408501693176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200304%2F_2020030408501693176.jpg&h=afd5ca80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4264345ce1cd6b62d21412589fba66b4816f9ef8","tid":1909593,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"戴口罩影大合照個3條友咩意思?<br />\n人地律師會會長同你影相<br />\n你唔畀面呀?"},{"pid":"a1e3cfe7e9bb4463612c27ff2a3020c728a52251","tid":1909593,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"好慘 得tvb幾丁友"},{"pid":"402d746ad8e984c9dfa92e36d44531f15f023178","tid":1909593,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"律屍會不嬲都奶共"},{"pid":"22f10c1b7a80a31328be8be340ca2c7d2eb421de","tid":1909593,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"Law Soc班老屎忽真係夠撚晒垃圾 人地抗疫你就出黎搵明星唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c10c63a7b9036b62111fc9133a7aa2c6399714c","tid":1909593,"uid":58209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"大律師公會同律師會係兩樣野黎<br />\n律師會係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f3bea462a5c05a2b62b22ebbac63692830274f","tid":1909593,"uid":274722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"第一眼以為hana隔離係何君妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b18329c47574615af822905aa5b0008789c1f2"